msgstr ""

#: doc/en/get-started.md:5
msgid "**TGui** is a graphical interface for [Tarantool](https://www.tarantool.io/) that lets you create and manage data spaces (tables), link them, define computed columns or triggers, and compose declarative custom views (YAML)."
