#: doc/en/reference.md:921
msgid "2. TGui automatically computes a **diff** between the file's schema and the current schema, and displays it with color codes:"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:922
msgid "   - green **Create**: the item will be added."
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:923
msgid "   - red **Delete**: the item will be removed (Replace mode only)."
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:924
msgid "   - orange **Modify**: a field's type has changed."
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:925
msgid "3. Choose the **import mode** and confirm."
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:927
msgid "### Import modes"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:929
msgid "| Mode         | Behavior |"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:930
msgid "|--------------|----------|"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:931
msgid "| **Merge**    | Creates missing spaces, fields, relations, views, and groups. Existing items (same name) are left untouched. |"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:932
msgid "| **Replace**  | First deletes all existing spaces and groups, then recreates everything from the snapshot. Warning: all existing data is lost. |"
msgstr ""

#: doc/en/reference.md:934
msgid "The result indicates the number of items created, ignored, and any errors."
msgstr ""

